Lodi is here? - Aha"

9
00:01:09,502 --> 00:01:11,663
"Take your partners? - Aha"

10
00:01:11,871 --> 00:01:13,998
"Grasp the wrist of your beloved"

11
00:01:14,207 --> 00:01:16,300
"and never let it go? - Aha"

12
