You'll take zaara to atari
and see her onto her train. She's all alone...

116
00:10:46,779 --> 00:10:51,546
what if something happens to her?
- She's become your favourite in a day?

117
00:10:52,084 --> 00:10:55,713
You used to get upset when it was time
for me to leave and stop me

118
00:10:55,921 --> 00:11:00,221
Today you want me to leave quickly?
- I don't have time for your nonsense

119
00:11:01,193 --> 00:11:04,321
I've made some laddoos for
you and ranjit. Take them

120
00:11:09,902 --> 00:11:13,167
Oh Ginda where've you been?
- Veeru's getting late

121
00:11:13,372 --> 00:11:15,670
Bauji I was filling up diesel.
- Is this any time to fill up?

122
00:11:15,874 --> 00:11:17,000
Let it be

123
00:11:18,210 --> 00:11:18,835
Okay now bless me...

124
00:11:20,913 --> 00:11:21,845
May you live long, son

125
00:11:23,449 --> 00:11:24,507
Tell her, huh? - Yes yes, I'll tell her

126
00:11:24,716 --> 00:11:26,741
Shall I? - Stop pressurizing me

127
00:11:26,952 --> 00:11:27,884
Maati control him

128
00:11:28,187 --> 00:11:29,711
Where are you going?
What's in this?

129
00:11:29,922 --> 00:11:31,514
Not for you. - No...? I see...

130
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:34,725
for your son...?
- Bauji...

131
00:11:37,830 --> 00:11:40,697
What are you doing?
Here girls don't touch the feet

132
00:11:41,166 --> 00:11:44,192
But daughters ask for blessings before
they bid farewell to their fathers?

133
00:11:46,371 --> 00:11:47,201
May you live long my child

134
00:11:52,044 --> 00:11:55,343
Give your parents a message from me

135
00:11:57,282 --> 00:12:04,518
Tell them that a sixty year old Indian
salutes the values they've put into you

136
00:12:47,533 --> 00:12:49,933
What d'you think?
Will Veeru tell her?

137
00:12:50,636 --> 00:12:53,764
He's chaudhry Sumer Singh's son,
why won't he tell her...

138
00:12:54,540 --> 00:12:55,598
didn't I tell you?

139
00:12:56,441 --> 00:13:00,241
Stop it... - What... where're you going?
Listen...

140
00:13:09,721 --> 00:13:12,053
Squadron Leader Veer Pratap Singh
thank you very much

141
00:13:12,758 --> 00:13:13,417
For what?

142
00:13:14,693 --> 00:13:16,388
In exchange for my one day...

143
00:13:16,929 --> 00:13:21,559
you've given me a lifetime of
memories and relationships

144
00:13:22,167 --> 00:13:26,729
It was a promise from an Indian
to a Pakistani If I didn't fulfill it...

145
00:13:27,239 --> 00:13:29,469
my country's honour
would've been tarnished, no?

146
00:13:31,376 --> 00:13:34,812
I think getting Bebe's ashes here
was God's way to get me here

147
00:13:35,614 --> 00:13:40,074
I was destined to meet all of you.
- Do you believe in destiny?

148
00:13:41,353 --> 00:13:41,910
Of course

149
00:13:43,188 --> 00:13:46,385
don't you? - Not until now

150
00:13:47,693 --> 00:13:48,751
But now I've begun to believe

151
00:13:56,702 --> 00:13:57,532
are you all right?

152
