I'll keep it. I'll give it to you later

158
00:14:32,237 --> 00:14:33,704
come... hold on tight...

159
00:14:41,146 --> 00:14:43,046
How many times are you going
to save my life?

160
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:47,211
As many times you put yourself at risk...

161
00:15:30,195 --> 00:15:32,095
actually there's
a lot of hustle for seats

162
00:15:32,164 --> 00:15:33,426
The festival of Idd is coming up.
At this time...

163
00:15:33,598 --> 00:15:38,399
a lot of people go across the border.
But you don't worry, I'll find a way

164
00:16:04,796 --> 00:16:09,165
Thank God you're all right.
I just got off the train from Lahore

165
00:16:09,801 --> 00:16:12,099
I was finding out about Kiritpur,
when I saw you

166
00:16:14,039 --> 00:16:20,444
Your father has returned. He sent me.
Let's call home and say you're fine.

167
00:16:20,645 --> 00:16:22,272
Then we'll prepare for our return

168
00:16:25,517 --> 00:16:26,609
and you are...?

169
00:16:26,985 --> 00:16:30,284
This's Veer.
Squadron Leader Veer Pratap Singh

170
00:16:30,856 --> 00:16:36,522
Thanks to him, I've managed to get here.
This is raza. Raza Shirazi, my fiance

171
00:17:09,628 --> 00:17:12,119
The seats are done,
we should be leaving now...

172
00:17:14,499 --> 00:17:17,559
So silly of me... I went on talking
about everything...

173
00:17:18,069 --> 00:17:22,665
but I forgot to tell you of raza
- You made a big mistake.

174
00:17:23,542 --> 00:17:24,167
What!

175
00:17:28,413 --> 00:17:29,471
You made a big mistake

176
00:17:36,688 --> 00:17:43,719
zaara I'm a very simple man. I speak
frankly and understand things simply

177
00:17:45,130 --> 00:17:49,157
It's the first time I started thinking
differently because of Bauji and Maati

178
00:17:51,570 --> 00:17:55,336
The entire journey I kept thinking up
a way to stop you, not to let you go...

179
00:17:56,141 --> 00:18:03,479
and tell you that I really like you
and if you think I'm okay then...

180
00:18:03,682 --> 00:18:06,515
let's get married

181
00:18:09,221 --> 00:18:12,679
and we'll breeze through life together
just like these past two days

182
00:18:14,926 --> 00:18:16,223
But the guy up there has strange ways

183
00:18:17,062 --> 00:18:20,589
He kept building my confidence
and then when we got here...

184
00:18:21,766 --> 00:18:23,859
He changed the entire story

185
00:18:30,876 --> 00:18:35,040
You must be wondering why
I'm telling you all this right now

186
00:18:35,247 --> 00:18:42,676
please don't get me wrong. I understand
that you belong to someone else...

187
00:18:43,889 --> 00:18:49,885
and there's nothing between us
nor can there ever be...

188
00:18:52,831 --> 00:18:56,733
but where ever...
whenever you need a friend...

189
00:18:58,303 --> 00:19:02,569
just remember that there is a man
across the border...

190
00:19:03,675 --> 00:19:05,575
Who will give his life for you

191
00:19:13,685 --> 00:19:14,913
c'mon zaara we must leave

192
00:19:15,954 --> 00:19:16,579
Mr. Veer...

193
00:19:18,356 --> 00:19:23,089
zaara told me how you saved her life.
Now I'm indebted to you.

194
00:19:23,962 --> 00:19:28,661
So tell me how may I repay you?
- Just keep zaara happy...

195
00:19:29,768 --> 00:19:30,666
the debt will be repaid

196
00:19:31,369 --> 00:19:33,428
careful Mr. Veer...

197
00:19:33,972 --> 00:19:37,100
lest I get the impression
that you've fallen in love with zaara

198
00:19:39,711 --> 00:19:42,373
what is love... I don't know.
But yes...

199
00:19:44,316 --> 00:19:49,811
I do wish from the bottom of my heart
that zaara never has tears in her eyes

200
00:19:50,989 --> 00:19:52,115
That she always keeps smiling

201
00:19:54,159 --> 00:19:57,959
If that's what you call love,
then love it is

202
00:19:59,931 --> 00:20:06,803
Mr. Veer, you're talking about
my fiancee to my face

203
00:20:08,573 --> 00:20:13,408
I don't know whether to consider this
a compliment or an insult

204
00:20:15,413 --> 00:20:19,076
If you think of this as nothing,
it's better. For the truth is that...

205
00:20:20,185 --> 00:20:25,020
I'm nothing to her
and you are everything for her

206
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:32,655
Good Bye

207
00:20:34,032 --> 00:20:34,657
Let's go

208
