00:22:37,188 --> 00:22:41,750
"just for two moments existed
the story of our hearts"

221
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:48,263
"and then you went your way
and I went mine"

222
00:22:58,810 --> 00:23:00,038
"Seven eighty six"

223
00:23:04,415 --> 00:23:05,040
dinner time

224
00:23:07,785 --> 00:23:11,551
and Ma'am your visiting time is over

225
00:23:11,990 --> 00:23:13,287
You'll have to leave now

226
00:23:24,502 --> 00:23:25,469
I'll come back tomorrow

227
00:23:27,038 --> 00:23:30,201
Sorry, your story is left incomplete

228
00:23:30,842 --> 00:23:31,740
come on, Ma'am

