anything better than this

396
00:44:25,796 --> 00:44:28,788
Wow, you can see
the entire city from here

397
00:44:32,002 --> 00:44:34,869
There can't be a better room than this
in the whole of Lahore

398
00:44:37,808 --> 00:44:39,867
I didn't tell zaara
that you're coming

399
00:44:44,514 --> 00:44:46,072
