they'll start wondering where I am

408
00:45:16,847 --> 00:45:18,576
If you need anything Munir's here

409
00:45:22,185 --> 00:45:22,776
Thank you Shabbo

410
00:45:26,623 --> 00:45:32,186
I didn't think you'd come,
but now after meeting you...

411
00:45:32,662 --> 00:45:36,530
I'm sure you'll take zaara with you

412
00:45:38,335 --> 00:45:39,893
How could I not come?

413
00:45:40,003 --> 00:45:44,599
My Babuji says, true love happens
only once in a lifetime

