00:48:14,057 --> 00:48:17,959
"Like the moth dies on the flame..."

434
00:48:18,395 --> 00:48:26,598
"a besotted lover has
come to your door"

435
00:49:15,185 --> 00:49:21,818
"What a turn this story has taken"

436
00:49:22,192 --> 00:49:33,797
