462
00:52:35,151 --> 00:52:39,053
You can't go there and do anything.
Abbaji is in deep shock

463
00:52:39,255 --> 00:52:42,622
I am the cause for the shock
and the solution

464
00:52:44,394 --> 00:52:46,794
I hadn't come here just to see
zaara's face

465
00:52:48,498 --> 00:52:52,298
If nobody speaks,
there's bound to be silence

466
00:52:53,937 --> 00:53:01,469
Someone has to make the first move,
whether it brings on a storm or a wedding

467
00:53:59,569 --> 00:54:05,667
My name is Mariam Hayaat Khan.
I'm zaara's mother

468
00:54:07,243 --> 00:54:12,545
But perhaps today I have lost
the right to call her my own...

469
00:54:14,083 --> 00:54:16,381
because my daughter's
not mine anymore

470
00:54:17,587 --> 00:54:21,216
She's yours now

471
00:54:24,761 --> 00:54:27,229
I've come to ask you to give
my daughter back to me

472
00:54:28,598 --> 00:54:34,400
please give us back our daughter!
Otherwise her father will die

473
00:54:39,609 --> 00:54:44,410
He won't be able to bear the shame,
he'll die

474
00:54:47,717 --> 00:54:56,750
I've heard that you save lives...
you're the one who saved zaara's life

475
00:54:58,961 --> 00:55:03,421
So now please save her
father's life

476
00:55:06,069 --> 00:55:11,439
I beg of you, please save his life

477
00:55:14,143 --> 00:55:16,111
Else he'll die...

478
00:55:18,481 --> 00:55:20,108
he'll die...

479
00:55:23,419 --> 00:55:28,447
a mother never has to beg to her son,
she just has to order

480
00:55:32,428 --> 00:55:36,330
zaara has always and will
always belong to you

481
00:55:40,503 --> 00:55:45,202
did you think that I would've taken
zaara away without your permission?

482
00:55:49,178 --> 00:55:57,381
People say that love is blind,
so we were also blinded by our love

483
00:55:58,988 --> 00:56:04,119
We could only see each other
We didn't see if we were harming anyone...

484
00:56:05,495 --> 00:56:09,295
hurting anyone or...

485
00:56:09,799 --> 00:56:11,426
if someone's life was at stake...

486
00:56:13,870 --> 00:56:15,201
we couldn't see anything

487
00:56:17,573 --> 00:56:19,165
But now everything's clear

488
00:56:20,910 --> 00:56:29,841
Love can't be more important
than someone's life. Don't you worry...

489
00:56:31,621 --> 00:56:37,184
zaara will marry the person
of her parent's choice

490
00:56:39,195 --> 00:56:42,722
You prepare for the wedding.
I'll talk to zaara

491
00:56:46,802 --> 00:56:53,366
I promise you that she will
willingly agree to the marriage

492
00:57:02,418 --> 00:57:06,548
Is every son from
your country like you?

493
00:57:09,759 --> 00:57:10,885
I don't know that

494
00:57:12,528 --> 00:57:18,728
But yes every mother in my country
is exactly like you

495
00:58:14,690 --> 00:58:17,158
If you think that I've made
a wrong decision...

496
00:58:19,295 --> 00:58:25,325
then just tell me. No one will be able
to stop me from taking you to India

497
00:58:32,541 --> 00:58:34,509
Your decision is absolutely right

498
00:58:36,712 --> 00:58:39,180
This has happened because of
one silly mistake on my part

499
00:58:40,883 --> 00:58:44,512
I'd made a promise to myself
that I won't break

500
00:58:45,721 --> 00:58:47,848
If only I'd been able to stop myself
when I saw you yesterday...

501
00:58:48,057 --> 00:58:48,682
That...

502
00:58:50,893 --> 00:58:54,522
one silly mistake of yours will heIp
get me through the rest of my life

503
00:58:57,900 --> 00:59:04,533
If you'd taken that away from me
then what would I take back with me?

504
00:59:07,677 --> 00:59:09,542
Why is God doing this to us?

505
00:59:10,413 --> 00:59:12,881
I've never done anything wrong
in my life

506
00:59:13,749 --> 00:59:15,876
So why is he punishing me like this...?

507
00:59:24,593 --> 00:59:28,791
I'm keeping two moments of
your life with me

508
00:59:32,468 --> 00:59:34,402
and I'm giving two moments
of my life to you

509
00:59:37,606 --> 00:59:39,574
These two moments are the symbol
of our love

510
00:59:41,110 --> 00:59:42,907
These two moments make our love story

511
00:59:46,449 --> 00:59:49,418
Now we'll live our lives on
these two moments...

512
00:59:53,622 --> 00:59:58,491
but with a smile

513
01:00:02,665 --> 01:00:04,599
Neither will our love weaken

514
01:00:07,870 --> 01:00:09,462
Nor will our duties
remain unfulfilled

515
01:00:15,745 --> 01:00:20,648
You'll honour your parents
by being a good wife

516
01:00:22,585 --> 01:00:27,318
and I'll fulfill Bauji's dreams
back in the village

517
01:00:31,694 --> 01:00:37,132
and after you've had
eight-ten children...

518
01:00:38,234 --> 01:00:39,496
you bring everyone along
for a visit

519
01:00:41,637 --> 01:00:48,475
I'll take you for a ride on a cycle
and show you a new village

520
01:00:52,181 --> 01:00:56,311
But after having eight-ten kids
I won't be able to sit on a cycle

521
01:00:59,388 --> 01:01:05,293
Yes, you've got a point.
Then I'll arrange for a tractor
